ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Broad overview of autoimmunity. Each session goes over a different area in the field, and covers some key papers. I would recommend the class to another student because it allowed me to learn more about major mechanisms behind autoimmunity and the current state of the field. The grant writing process was also a good experience.
IBIO 537 is a good seminar course that focuses on issues related to autoimmunity. I recommend this course if you are interested in autoimmune diseases.
